data.description: Welcome to your dream home, nestled in the sought-after community of Poquoson, Virginia. This property offers a rare opportunity to own a piece of coastal paradise with gorgeous views, top-rated schools, and a charming small-town environment. Enjoy the peace of mind that comes with recent updates, including replacement windows, a newer roof, and a new HVAC system. This home has a large backyard, stainless steel appliances, a kitchen with a breakfast bar, and spacious dining/living areas. Relax with your morning coffee on the front porch or with a good book by your stunning hearthstone fireplace. Location is everything, with a short commute to Langley, NASA, and more. Don't wait! See this one before it's gone! Closing cost assistance available!
